languages.text: "Вы видали?! Нас едва не сбили в воздухе! Ох какому-то безрукому идиоту не повезет сегодня, когда его притащат к Лорд-капитану на дознание и суд!"
"Did you see that? They almost knocked us out of the air! Some bumbling idiot's going to regret that when he's dragged before the Lord Captain for questioning and trial!"

languages.text: “你看到了吗？他们差点就把我们从天上打下来了！等到某个蠢货被拖到舰长大人面前，接受盘问与审判时，他一定会后悔！”
languages.original_text: "Did you see that? They almost knocked us out of the air! Some bumbling idiot's going to regret that when he's dragged before the Lord Captain for questioning and trial!"

languages.text: «¿Ha visto eso? ¡Casi nos derriban! ¡Un pobre idiota va a lamentarlo cuando le arrastren frente a{mf|l| la} Lord Capitán para su interrogatorio y juicio!».
languages.original_text: "Did you see that? They almost knocked us out of the air! Some bumbling idiot's going to regret that when he's dragged before the Lord Captain for questioning and trial!"

languages.text: 「あれを見た？危うく空中に叩き出されるところだったわ！あのバカたち、尋問と裁判のためにロード・キャプテンの前に引っ張り出されて、後悔するといいわ！」
languages.original_text: "Did you see that? They almost knocked us out of the air! Some bumbling idiot's going to regret that when he's dragged before the Lord Captain for questioning and trial!"

traits.speaker: IdiraCompanion

languages.text: "Habt Ihr das gesehen? Sie hätten uns fast abgeschossen! Irgendein ungeschickter Idiot wird das bereuen, wenn er vor den Lord Captain geschleift wird, um verhört und abgeurteilt zu werden!"

languages.text: « Vous avez vu ça ? On a manqué valser ! L'idiot responsable va le regretter quand il sera traîné devant {mf|le seigneur-capitaine|la seigneure-capitaine} pour être interrogé et jugé ! »
